# Commits & PRs

- Use **Conventional Commits** (`feat:`, `fix:`, `chore:`, etc.). Keep commits scoped and descriptive.
- Open PRs early; keep them small. Include a short test plan and screenshots for UI changes.
- Reference issues/cards; link to docs/ADRs when relevant.
